						<summary>

						<p>The first portion is in the nature of a duplicate of the above inscription. The next portion states that <hi rend="bold">Chandrāditya</hi> also established a garden called <hi rend="italic">Chandrādityanandanavanam.</hi> Eight persons are named as witnesses to these charities.</p>						

						<p>First Side.</p>						

